            "title": "盤中速報 - 熙特爾-創(7740)急拉3.64%報227.0元，成交90張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>熙特爾-創(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:7740:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/7740\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">7740-TW</a>)近5分K漲速3.64%，08日09:13報227.0元，成交90張，今日漲幅為3.65％。（註：漲跌速為5分K的漲跌幅）</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>熙特爾-創(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:7740:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/7740\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">7740-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲2.58%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-33 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-35 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+2 張</li> </ul></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main>",
